This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) techniques to identify the causes of aviation safety incidents. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with NLP and related topics. The paper also uses machine learning algorithms, which are covered in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques, which are covered in cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper deals with cybersecurity, which is covered in cs.CY (Computers and Society).
